    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10886: Report engineering DLL version in console and ituff'
'Merged PR 10779: Cheery Pick for Prime Tickets'
'Merged PR 10787: VoltageService - Allow for setting ratios in FLAME mode (and overriding ratios in for pat mod configs)'
'Merged PR 10466: Merged PR 10345: [FuseDb][PatConfig][Functional] Accept pin group as pin alias.'
'Merged PR 10385: [57696] [PatConfigService] OnTheFlyHandleWithData to use configurable ConsoleService - 13xxxx'
'Merged PR 10089: [56784] [Prime.Services.PatConfigService] Move PatConfig BackgroundQueue prints to Telemetry'
'Merged PR 10038: [PatConfigService]  PatConfig service patch 13.1.1 changes to 13.xx.xx'</releaseNotes>
